narratives.question_text: What was valuable about the format and content of this class?
comments: It is good to know different art styles and the way to convey art. Also I enjoy that we share our works with different major students. It helps me that to be open to practice different way to express my ideas.
I enjoyed the wide variety of speakers in different fields and the final presentations.
Everything. The more the merrier. This class was a visual and information overload and I wish I could take it all three years.

The variety of guests that came was one of my favorite parts about this class. It was very useful to listen to the diffednt artists and what they do, their philosophy, how they work, etc. Also seeing everyone's presentations for the last 2 classes was great. I really enjoy having people from other schools in this class.
I expect to see more art lectures.
I would have liked for the professor to lead a couple more discussions.
It's pretty crowded in that tiny room

narratives.question_text: Please provide any other constructive comments.
comments: It was a good experience to take the course with students from different schools.
